Introduction

The Norwegian Directorate of Fisheries (FDir) and Institute of Marine Research (IMR) use abbreviations, codes and definitions in their data. This document contains tables of definition files within the RstoxUtils package.

Norwegian Directorate of Fisheries

The codes have been extracted from the Norwegian Directorate of Fisheries website.

Cruise series list

The cruiseSeriesList can be used to connect cruises in the Biotic data with their respective cruise series. The BioticExplorerServer package does this automatically allowing database search using cruise series. You can update the list with the prepareCruiseSeriesList() function while connected to IMR intranet.
